title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 26 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 26 2022
description:
Alabama Senate candidate, Congressman Mo Brooks joins C&B to discuss the left's attempted gun grab, immigration and the midterm elections. Serial kneeler, Colin Kaepernick attempts to return to the NFL with the Raiders. Any team that signs him, will have lots of "woke insurance”. Live coverage of Uvalde Texas Police Chief Daniel Rodriguez’s press conference, many haunting questions still remain.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
